# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# ── Go build artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Compiled binary (any name at root)
/bot-go
/cicd-bot

# Go temp / local GOPATH overrides
.gopath/
.go-tmp/
temp/

# ── Node.js (legacy) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/node_modules
dist/
/build
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml
*.tsbuildinfo

# ── Environment ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env*
!.env.example

# ── Database / data ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/data
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# ── Misc ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
*.pem
repomix-output.xml
logs.txt
__pycache__

# ── Agent / tooling ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/agent-memory/
.claude/hooks/.logs/
.claude/settings.bak.json
.gemini/settings.json
.serena/cache
.opencode/
plans/**/*
